msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroRito_Desc"
msgid ""
"The scattered One-Hit Obliterator led you to a\n"
"location where a stone monument with a map of\n"
"trials appeared. Kass's song seems related...\n"
"\n"
"One, <1.se_co>shoot the flame dragon's horn<2.re_co>.\n"
"Two, <3.se_co>race down a peak rings adorn<4.re_co>.\n"
"Three, <5.se_co>shoot four targets to win<6.re_co>.\n"
"Champion, the trials begin!\n"
"\n"
"You still have <7.se_co>three<8.re_co> trials to complete."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroRito_Finish"
msgid ""
"You defeated the phantasm of Windblight\n"
"Ganon, which was born from your own\n"
"memories and fears.\n"
"\n"
"Kass's composition, entitled <1.se_co>Champion Revali's\n"
"Song<2.re_co>, was so true and moving that it allowed\n"
"you to visualize a memory from 100 years ago.\n"
"\n"
"By conquering the trial, your sacred power has\n"
"increased and Revali's Gale has become\n"
"more efficient than ever."
msgstr ""

